  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">UNEP + World Bank: support for environmental sustainability in water resource management</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The UNEP component aims at strengthening the Water Unit in UNEP with special focus on integrated water resource management. Since 2002 Denmark has supported the Unit hosted by DHI and the Unit is by UNEP recognized as being a key infrastructure in UNEP in particular in relation to the renewed focus on water in formulating new sustainable development goals. 
The World Bank program Water Partnership Program aims at supporting innovation in the water management. The program supports development and fieldtests of new policies, strategies and technologies and has a proven track record of having influenced the large water portfolio of the World Bank.</narrative>
  </description>
